title: Launcher won't work.
body:
Yesterday I was playing league fine now every time i click the launcher it says.

"RADS Error


Unspecified error occurred. Please check the logs for more information. "

any info on how to fix this would be helpful. Reinstalling didn't work.

replies.body:
If nothing else seems to help, this error usually indicates an issue with the patcher itself, such as it being corrupted.  Make sure to complete all of the steps in our [Patching Issues Article](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434).  It has the most common solutions that should resolve this error and get you back into the client.

Give me a heads up if the steps don't seem to resolve it!
My client simply don't appear and I tryed all what the support said to do, nothing work
